title: Amazing 2/2 condo
posting_body: ['The living is easy in this amazing 2/2 property perfectly situated in the heart of Pembroke Pines.', 'With a water view and gated community, this condo is perfect for any family!', 'It has carpeted and tiled floors and an enclosed screened entrance.', 'The unit has stainless steel appliances and built-in wooden cabinets.', 'Other highlights of the property include central air, a community pool, a clubhouse, and water is also included.', 'With transport, schools, shops, dining & leisure facilities within easy reach, this is the ideal place to call home.', 'Be prepared for this to be love at first sight!', 'Common Area Security Deposit equivalent to one month of rent from tenant made payable to HOA.', '8842 SW 3rd St # 202 PEMBROKE PINES, FL 33025-1492', 'PROPERTY ID:  GTA11241648', 'Type of Property: condo', 'List Price:\t$2,200', 'Bedrooms:  2', 'Bathrooms: 2', 'SqFt (Liv):¤945', 'CALL OR TEXT TODAY', 'show contact info', 'Global Trust Realty, LLC posts properties for a 30 day period of time.', ' Due to current high rental demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', ' All prices are subject to change based upon availability.', 'All information is deemed to be correct but not guaranteed.', 'Listed and Brokered by:Keller Williams Realty SW']
